{"sequence":127,"timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:38:24.624405903Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-5-61c8456d","body":"finding_summary: The tmux-specific regression test for stdout-only exhaustion is still disabled with `#[ignore]`, so normal `cargo test` runs do not cover the exact adapter path that now falls back to raw stdout in `src/adapters/tmux.rs:633-643`.\nseverity: low\naffected_files:\n- tests/unit/tmux_adapter_test.rs:414-416\n- src/adapters/tmux.rs:633-643\nremediation_hint: Remove the `#[ignore]` on `tmux_adapter_classifies_stdout_only_exhaustion_as_backend_exhausted`; it already passes when run explicitly, so the shipped suite can enforce the intended `BackendExhausted` classification on the tmux path.","dedup_key":"2036541602d586745c9485c038e1e62ccd9118012b18015a8e73b10927283ef8","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260414001056","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":128,"timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:38:24.633854869Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-5-ce60c997","body":"The tmux test `tmux_adapter_classifies_stdout_only_exhaustion_as_backend_exhausted` at tests/unit/tmux_adapter_test.rs:415 has `#[ignore = \"requires gsp bead fix: stdout-only exhaustion not yet classified as BackendExhausted\"]`. This IS the gsp bead — the fix is fully implemented in tmux.rs (lines 633-636 now use stdout_for_exit_failure_classification). The #[ignore] must be removed so the regression test actually runs. Without this, the acceptance criterion 'Regression test covers stdout-only exhaustion path' is only half-met: the process_backend integration test runs, but the tmux adapter path is never exercised.","dedup_key":"a30e958640f9ece7fa99f400197fdde803be7989db9cc0545173dd5a0d3915c8","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"claude","model_id":"claude-opus-4-6-max","reviewer_id":"reviewer-2"}],"run_id":"run-20260414001056","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
